title: Is There An Age Limit For This Well-Know App?
description:
Our intern Mackenzie is conflicted about an app she currently uses. She downloaded it when she was in middle school. She still uses it constantly to talk to her friends, but it's starting to feel juvenile to her. Is she too old for this app?
